metadata.name: CYBR2088 #1
metadata.description: "Introducing the 'CYBR2088' NFT collection, featuring stunning digital art depicting youths of the future. These one-of-a-kind pieces showcase futuristic facial features, high-tech clothing and accessories, and a unique blend of human and robotic elements. Each NFT in this collection is a must-have for sci-fi and cyberpunk fans, and is sure to make a bold statement in any digital art collection."
